name: Mondays crowd
description:
Monday is the busiest day of the week. After Friday night to Sunday off work, Monday is the day when office activities begin to return.

This photo was taken at the commuterline station in the afternoon, when everyone who was working was going home. scrambled to get on the train so they could get home as soon as possible.

but after the covid-19 pandemic, this atmosphere never happened again. because people had to keep their distance, some offices had to "work from home", and some people lost their jobs.

This photo is from a video I recorded when I left to meet friends at the cafe.
